testsuite.name: com.tim.one.service.AccountServiceIntegrationSpec

testcase.name: When we have an user with 100 and trama account with 1000 and we transfer 100 from trama to user, we expect that user has 200 and trama has 900
When we have an user with 0 and trama account with 50 and we transfer 25 from trama to user, we expect that user has 25 and trama has 25
When we have an user with 100 and trama account with 0 and we transfer 100 from trama to user, we expect class com.tim.one.exception.BusinessException
When we have an user with 100 and trama account with 500 and we transfer 0 from trama to user, we expect class com.tim.one.exception.BusinessException
When we have an user with 100 and trama account with 500 and we transfer -100 from trama to user, we expect class com.tim.one.exception.BusinessException
